title: Ocean City man aids swimmers caught in riptide off Nantucket
text:
Ocean City man aids swimmers caught in riptide off Nantucket Father and daughter caught in riptide, captured it on camera 
Derrick Johns, of Austin, Texas, went for a swim at Nobadeer beach Tuesday afternoon with his 16-year-old, daughter, Erynn Johns, who was holding a GoPro on a selfie stick and managed to capture the ordeal on video. 
Derrick Johns, of Austin, Texas, went for a swim at Nobadeer beach Tuesday afternoon with his 16-year-old, daughter, Erynn Johns, who was holding a GoPro on a selfie stick and managed to capture the ordeal on video. The Baltimore Sun 
An Ocean City man came to the rescue of a father and daughter who were caught in a riptide off the coast of Massachusetts, The Boston Globe reports .
